comments: Replay review pursuant to a coach's challenge of the foul on Tucker (HOU) is deemed unsuccessful.  Tucker is not established in a legal guarding position in Brogdon's (IND) path at the time of the contact.
Nwaba (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Brogdon (IND).
Harden (HOU) makes marginal contact with Sabonis (IND) during his shot attempt.
Harden (HOU) makes marginal contact with Brogdon (IND) before stepping back for the shot attempt.
Sabonis (IND) and Gordon (HOU) briefly engage and separate off-ball.
Tucker (HOU) makes marginal contact with Brogdon (IND) during his driving shot attempt.
Tucker (HOU) sets the screen on Brogdon (IND) and does not deliver contact.
Turner (IND) cleanly blocks Nwaba's (HOU) shot attempt.
Nwaba (HOU) commits a take foul on Brogdon (IND).
Turner (IND) cleanly dislodges the ball from Wall (HOU) during the drive.
Wall (HOU) makes incidental contact with Sabonis (IND) after the ball is loose.
Tucker (HOU) commits a take foul on Oladipo (IND).
